      <title>热带风暴黛比穿过墨西哥湾向佛罗里达进发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/forecasters-expect-depression-to-become-tropical-storm-debby-as-it-nears-florida-s-gulf-coast</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迈阿密（美联社）——周六，一股热带低气压在古巴北部增强为热带风暴黛比，据最新预测，它穿过墨西哥湾并与佛罗里达州相撞时将增强为飓风。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-08-03/forecasters-expect-depression-to-become-tropical-storm-debby-as-it-nears-florida-s-gulf-coast</guid>
